  <!--
    Reviewed suppressions (Chapter 16: suppress with a reason, never disable a whole detector).

    This module has none. Its types are immutable records and small value/port classes, so the
    representation-exposure detectors (EI_EXPOSE_REP / EI_EXPOSE_REP2) stay quiet on their own. The
    structure demonstrations carry no mutable shared state to defend by copying. The filter is kept
    (empty) so a future, genuinely reviewed suppression has a home with a stated reason rather than
    being added inline.
  -->
</FindBugsFilter>
